text: Astrid Johanna Grents (born 14 May 1998) is an Estonian Muay Thai martial artist. == Career == She competed at the 2022 IFMA World Muaythai Championships finishing third, and 2023 European Games winning a gold medal in the Women's 60 kg class. == References == Category:1998 births Category:Martial artists Category:Estonian sportspeople
title: Astrid Johanna Grents
